    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1769005364\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1769005364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Nova Hyper 是一款包含故事模式和Rouguelike模式的卡牌构筑类战斗游戏。获取新卡牌，构筑属于你的”强到爆”卡组！你能打败无敌的女王吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗 → 获得卡牌 → 调整卡组 → 重复此过程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/fc2b98b0b24436e7fbc6be183e18de3b.poster.avif?t=1769005364\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/fc2b98b0b24436e7fbc6be183e18de3b.webm?t=1769005364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/fc2b98b0b24436e7fbc6be183e18de3b.mp4?t=1769005364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>使用战术击败你的对手来获得金钱，可以用来购买或升级卡片。用这些手段巧妙地构筑你的卡组，你就可以快速增强实力来击败更强大的对手，获取更多金钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用Nova Hyper，一转攻势！！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/a3d57b0086c81c88d2c319c8feb99280.poster.avif?t=1769005364\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197330/extras/a3d57b0086c81c88d2c319c8feb99280.webm?t=1769005364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当情况不妙时，快使用Nova Hyper! 这会给予你各种增益效果来扭转乾坤。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过请记住，你的对手也可以使用它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与伙伴和对手们一同踏上挑战女王的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格鲜明的角色们怀着各自的理由，在前进的道路上等待着你。通过与他们对战来了解他们并成为伙伴。他们会是你打败无敌女王的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
